text: Qingdao is taking the lead in the number of people getting the Covid-19 vaccine. According to stats by the end of April 3, the city has vaccinated 1.2 million people, among which, 1 million has finished the 1st shot of the two-shot vaccine. #qingdao #china #vaccine #COVID19 https://t.co/UNt0MUf3iV
